===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[pole]] [[vault]]'''

#{{sports}} a [[jumping]] event contested in [[track and field]] which requires an [[athlete]] to carry a [[fiberglass]] [[pole]] down a [[runway]], [[plant]] the [[pole]] into a [[vaulting box]] and [[vault]] over a [[fiberglass]] [[bar]], landing on a [[matted]] [[pit]]

